         <div type="commentary">
            <head>Commentary</head>
            <p>The only obvious explanation is that Ptolemais was refounded with the new name 
               Eleutheropolis which has left no trace in the literary record; cf. the refoundation of Cyrenae as Claudiopolis by Claudius Gothicus <ref type="inscription">C07400</ref></p>
